10:45.740 --> 10:51.940
Looking into the interoperability Europe solutions might help them to see, okay, if this is here in the catalogue,

10:51.940 --> 10:56.540
this might be something when I built my software that it fits with those interoperability Europe solutions,

10:56.540 --> 11:00.580
that might be easier for public administrations to reuse it.

11:00.660 --> 11:10.020
