11:10.020 --> 11:16.380
And for now, between public administration, sharing is not a default and proper territory solutions are a default.

11:16.380 --> 11:24.780
And if you want to share among the solutions, then the IT people go to the lawyers of this world and I'm one of them so I can talk better about them.

11:24.780 --> 11:29.180
And they will ask those people, yeah, can we please, can we share?

11:29.180 --> 11:30.900
There's somebody else wants to reuse it.

11:30.900 --> 11:35.300
